Class ParamMotors

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.officinerobotiche.serial.frame.AbstractFrame
      • it.officinerobotiche.serial.frame.motion.MotionFrame
        • it.officinerobotiche.serial.frame.motion.ParamMotors
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Jmessage

    public class ParamMotors
extends MotionFrame
    Definition parameters on robots. You can set radius and wheelbase on unicycle robot. Gain to convert value read from Input capture or QEI. Used IS to configure this data, in particular meter, radiand, radians to sec.
    Author:
    Raffaello Bonghi
